1. **olaparib Lynparza 2014** = first FDA PARP — germline BRCA-mutated ovarian. 2017 maintenance + 2018 1L SOLO-1 (BRCA-mutated 1L all-comer) → ovarian cancer paradigm 변화. PARP synthetic lethal HRD axis 정립. quantum-VQE 의 PARP1 NAD+ binding pocket fit.
