3. **rucaparib Rubraca 2016** = third PARP — germline + somatic BRCA + 2022 ATHENA-MONO 1L maintenance. HRD test + ARIEL 시리즈. quantum-VQE 의 3-PARP comparator.
4. **mirvetuximab soravtansine Elahere 2022** = first FDA folate receptor α (FRα) ADC ovarian. MIRASOL Phase 3 — platinum-resistant FRα-high ovarian. DM4 maytansinoid payload + cleavable linker. 2024 1L expansion. quantum-VQE 의 ADC Fab + payload scaffold fit.
5. **dostarlimab Jemperli 2021 + 2024** = anti-PD-1 ovarian + 2024 MMR-d expansion + endometrial overlap. IO ovarian (HRP 환자 fit). cross-cancer pan-tumor MMR-d framework.
6. **bevacizumab Avastin 2014 ovarian** = first FDA VEGF + ovarian + maintenance. GOG-218 + ICON-7 + 만성 paradigm. cross-cancer VEGF.
7. **WEE1 + ATR + ATM (research)** = DDR DNA damage response 만성 next-gen — adavosertib + ceralasertib + zatutibirib. PARP-resistant + HRP cohort 가 fit. quantum-VQE 의 kinase pocket leverage.
8. **CDH6 + B7-H3 + raludotatug deruxtecan + ifinatamab deruxtecan (research)** = next-gen ADC ovarian Phase 3. mirvetuximab 후 second-wave ADC.
9. **BRCA + HRD + germline + somatic + Lynch + 가족성** = cancer susceptibility paradigm. risk-reducing salpingo-oophorectomy 가 1차예방 → cross-preventive + women_obgyn_extension + inherited_adult fold.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ovarian cancer 임상 의미 한정.

